Medical Mission in South Bechuana-</div><div class="t m5e3 x11 h2b y32 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">land, and helped the Helderberg College to erect a new music studio. These worthy </div><div class="t m68c x11 h2b ya2 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">projects have been a great blessing. </div><div class="t m7f0 x14 h2b yaea ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As our Sabbath school members give &quot;as God hath prospered&quot; them on December </div><div class="t md5 x11 h2b y60a ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">27, may it be a liberal offering for the establishment of mission stations for Zululand </div><div class="t m8bc x11 h2b y6c5 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and for Nyasaland! </div><div class="t m2634 x2a h2b yb06 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">40 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
